You fool! The wholesale slaughter of an entire city? Changing
them into mindless golems for your own piece of mind?!

GabText IS THAT ALL YOU'VE GOT?!
What's that old expression? Ah yes!
Kill me. Just.. just do it.
Kill you? No, \C[4]Auryn\C[0]. I have a better idea.
What.. what did you do to me? Will I die?
I've stopped your aging process. You'll never age a day beyond
today. Maybe after you've lived a couple hundred years, maybe after
you've held a few of your own loved ones as they pass into oblivion...
Maybe after you've seen how hell-bent you humans are to destroy
each other. Maybe then you'll understand how right I really am.
The paralysis will wear off in an hour. See yourself out
or I'll have my \C[14]Stone Wardens\C[0] throw you out.
No.. you can't. Come back here!
